3.0.0

Release Date: December 17, 2025
Milestone: Phase 5A Complete - Shopping Cart & Order Management System

Features:
- ✅ Backend Foundation (Clean Architecture, Database, Redis, Middleware)
- ✅ Authentication System (JWT, User Management, Security, Rate Limiting)
- ✅ Product Management (CRUD Operations, Advanced Filtering, Price Management)
- ✅ Shopping Cart (Guest Support, Cart Merging, 7-Day Expiration)
- ✅ Order Management (Status Workflow, Admin Dashboard, Pricing Logic)

New in v3.0.0:
- Complete Shopping Cart System (8 API endpoints)
- Order Management Framework (6 API endpoints)
- Guest Cart Support with Token Authentication
- 7-Day Cart Expiration System
- Cart Merging Functionality
- Professional Order Status Workflow
- Admin Dashboard with Statistics
- Comprehensive Address Management
- Real-time Cart Total Calculations
- Stock Reservation System
- Role-Based Order Management

